descriptionHtml:
Are you a fan of Siren Head SCP creepypasta? Then u need to get this application to help yourself with Creepy Monster called Siren Head 2 mobile game.
Siren Head is most scariest game of last months, eveyone trying to figure out where did he come from, who created him, and is this SCP, or Creepypasta monster?
We collected informtaions from sites, wikis etc... and put all of those in this awesome application, so after you download it u'll be really professional player of Siren Head game and know eveyrthing about scary story of Siren Head 2.
Find solution for every ingame puzzle in this app, dont waste your time to watch on YT, or searching in websites, here s everything in just one application with low weight.
The first photo of Siren Head he made was the one featuring Siren Head at a graveyard, in which he wrote a story about. Henderson also mentioned that Siren Head is very similar to the famous creepypasta character today known as Slender Man, as both of the characters got edited into real-life photos with a story being written regarding them.According to Henderson, people all over the world started sending their own photos to Henderson, with the intention of having Siren Head or another cryptid made by Henderson get added into the image.
So from those informations we can think that Siren Head game can be a some Slenderman form, its creepypasta from few years ago.U have to extract conclusions alone, every can think in other ways, so make your own Siren Head history.
Henderson also goes on to explain that Siren Head isn’t a human, although Siren Head does have a voice and can possibly speak a language. Specifically, Siren Head does not have any eyes, so it is possible that Siren Head uses other senses in order to orientate in space (like echolocation), though Siren Head’s use of camouflage says otherwise. However, Trevor has stated Siren Head does not actually need eyes, ears, a nose, or the ability to feel vibrations to be able to find prey due to his supernatural nature. He has also confirmed that Siren Head is not of this reality.
There s also many articles to read about Sirenhead, u'll find photos of this monster, videos and more informations about Henderson and hes history.
Of course also Full Guide for Siren Head 2 mobile game, so get this app, share it for friends and show everyone new news about Siren Head mobile !
